@{
    Layout = null;
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="description" content="About the photoblog of Clint McMahon — a software developer in Minneapolis." />
    <title>About — Clint McMahon Photos</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/classic-photoblog.css?v=3" />
    <script defer data-domain="clintmcmahon.com" src="https://plausible.io/js/script.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="pb-header">
        <a href="https://photos.clintmcmahon.com" class="pb-site-name">Clint McMahon</a>
        <span class="pb-header-byline">photographs from the life of <a href="https://clintmcmahon.com" class="pb-header-byline-link">clintmcmahon.com</a></span>
        <a href="https://photos.clintmcmahon.com" class="pb-header-nav">&#8592; photos</a>
    </header>

    <main class="pb-main">
        <div class="pb-about">
            <h1 class="pb-about-heading">About</h1>
            <div class="pb-about-body">
                <p>Minneapolis. Software by trade, photographs by habit.</p>
                <p>
                    This is a photoblog — a running record of what caught my attention.
                    Nothing curated, nothing thematic. The in-between moments of a life
                    lived mostly in the midwest, occasionally elsewhere.
                </p>
                <p>
                    I'm Clint McMahon, a software developer and consultant. I spend most
                    of my working hours writing .NET applications and helping companies
                    build things that actually run. More of that at
                    <a href="https://clintmcmahon.com">clintmcmahon.com</a>.
                </p>
                <p>
                    The photography here is incidental, which is maybe the point.
                    No studio, no planned shots — just what was in front of me on a given
                    day and whether I thought it was worth keeping.
                </p>
                <p>New photographs appear whenever something is.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <footer class="pb-footer">
            <nav class="pb-footer-nav">
                <a href="/photos/rss" class="pb-footer-link">RSS</a>
                <a href="https://clintmcmahon.com" class="pb-footer-link">clintmcmahon.com</a>
            </nav>
        </footer>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
